### ============================
### TEST QUERIES
### ============================

### Get all authors
GET http://localhost:8080/authors

###

### Get all books
GET http://localhost:8080/books

###

### Find author by name
GET http://localhost:8080/authors/name/J.K. Rowling

###

### Find books by author name
GET http://localhost:8080/books/author/Jules Verne
### Create A book
POST http://localhost:8080/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "His Last Bow",
  "authorId" : -3
  }
